reviews.headline: I buy these often.
reviews.comments: Doesn't flake as bad some.  I have lots of allergies and this one is good.

reviews.headline: Volume it is
reviews.comments: My eyelashes are very flat even after I curl them but after using Hypnose Drama Extreme volumizing mascara the are fuller with a lot of volume. Smudge proof and the volume last all day. The beauty about it is that you don't need to apply many lays for it to work.

reviews.headline: Clumpy thick lashes
reviews.comments: Very disappointed in this mascara. Too much comes out all at once and my lashes are thick and clumpy. The only way for me to control it is to use a tissue and pull a lot of the makeup off of the brush before I even attempt to put the mascara on. I had a sample of a different lancome mascara which I loved and this was definitely not it. Waste of money.

reviews.headline: This Lives Up To The Hype!
reviews.comments: I read all of the reviews and they sounded really good. I desperately needed some new mascara. So I tried this and love it. I even paid full price for it and it was worth every penny. Try it I think you will love it!

reviews.headline: Love love it!!
reviews.comments: I purchased the travel size to see if it will give my lashes volume, I am very pleased and will be purchasing the normal size.

reviews.headline: Cake-y but good volume!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This waterproof mascara is great! I stays on but I don't have to scrub too hard to get it off. It gives me great volume and is buildable too. The only thing I don't 'love' is that when I take the wand out of the tube, I am constantly scraping off excessive product back into the tube because otherwise it makes your lashes super cake-y.

reviews.headline: Smears crazy
reviews.comments: This mascara was great when first applying and the lashes look beaitiful, but it will give you raccoon eyes throughtout day. It will smudge faster if its hot and you're sweating

reviews.headline: Not bad
reviews.comments:
Was really hoping to get nice, smooth, non-clumpy mascara and lashes. But noooooooo.
It was clumpy and didn't stay on my eyelashes. It was under them when I got to my destination. : /

reviews.headline: Best Mascara
reviews.comments: I have used Chanel Mascara about 20 years, have tried others and always went back-until now .  This mascara creates volume, and easily removes.  No turning back.

reviews.headline: Gorgeous, deeply pigmented mascara
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] Lancôme products represent affordable luxury and this mascara also encompasses that same aesthetic. From the shape of the tube and the fluffy brush, the deep pigmented product and dramatic results this mascara is a great addition to your collection. The issue I have with it is its easily transferable, with some patience and allowing time to dry you can avoid this issue but I usually only have a few minutes to finish up my makeup and often don't have time to wait for it too fully dry down.

reviews.headline: Not a fan
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I wasn't a fan of this as it flaked and smeared on me a lot. It applied easily and came off just as easy. I prefer waterproof with me wearing contacts. Makes for less flaking.

reviews.headline: dramatic!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I really enjoyed this mascara from Lancome Hypnose Drama Mascara.I love the dramatic look! Exactly my style. This does not flake in my experience. It's long lasting, and it holds a curl for me.

reviews.headline: This has potential
reviews.comments: This mascara is promising…if you only use 1 coat. Anything more and there's major clumps. Its not really black either, more of a dark grey color. Started smudging within a couple of hours. I think if they updated the formula a bit this would be a good mascara! As it is now, i would not recommend.

reviews.headline: New Regular on the Team!!
reviews.comments: I don't have to wear false lashes and they look full and beautiful while wearing 2 coats! Love this mascara!

reviews.headline: Love Lancome Mascaras
reviews.comments: I received this product complimentary to try and review. I've always loved Lancome mascaras and monsieur big mascara was my go to mascara when I did not have eyelash extensions so I had high hopes for this product. I really enjoyed this mascara. It did not disappoint. As mentioned before, I do wear eyelash extensions, but I did use it in my lower lashes and my mother did try it as well and we both liked it. It coats and separates the lashes very well and does not flake off during the day. I would definitely purchase again.

reviews.headline: It was Great !
reviews.comments: I love it.

reviews.headline: irritating and highly fragranced
reviews.comments: caused my eye to itch and become swollen. the fragrance in this product is super intense as well.

reviews.headline: Buildable and lengthening
reviews.comments: This product did a great job lengthening my lashes and is really behaved and didn't crumble underneath my eyes throughout the day. Went on a little think but was able to build it up without issue or clumping. Would purchase for future.

reviews.headline: This is seriously the best mascara I've ever used
reviews.comments: I am in love with this mascara. It lengthens my lashes more than any other mascara I've ever used (Dior, Better Than Sex, Greatlash by Maybelline, Sky High, and more).

reviews.headline: Loved it until I didn't
reviews.comments: I loved this mascara at first, especially the wand, but then my eyes started having an allergic reaction that caused eczema on my eyelids, there's also a strong perfume fragrance I did not like and I found it smudged everywhere in the extreme heat of Arizona.

faceoff_positive.comments:
I would like to preface this review by saying that I was generously gifted a Lancôme Hypnôse Drama Mascara from Bzz Agent in exchange for my honest opinion of the product. As a mascara enthusiast, I've tried too many to count all over the years, from drugstore brands to department store brands. Lancôme Hypnôse Drama Mascara has truly stood out. Let me break down 5 key standout features that impressed me about this mascara and why I feel it deserves a spot in your beauty routine.
**Amplifies Volume:** I saw a significant difference in just ONE coat, which turned my lashes into dramatic, voluminous beauties. The formula provides impressive volume without feeling or looking heavy or clumping, creating a striking "fuller-than-life" effect. 
**Holds Curl:** One of its standout features is the ability to maintain a curl all day. The curved brush lifts and curls each lash effortlessly, giving my eyes a wide-awake, captivating look. I didn't use my eyelash curler prior to applying this mascara and I don't need to with this formula! Another plus! 
**Adds Length:** If you're looking for long, fluttery lashes, this mascara delivers. Lancôme Hypnôse Drama Mascara lengthens my lashes significantly, adding a dramatic flair to my eye makeup, but they didn't look coated or thick.  
**Easy to Remove:** Despite its staying power, this mascara is very easy to remove. I used my cleanser and water at the end of the day and it came off effortlessly! 
**Clump-Free Application:** Nobody wants a mascara that clumps or flakes. Lancôme Hypnôse Drama Mascara provides a smooth, clump-free application every time, thanks to its innovative formula and precision brush.
In conclusion, Lancôme Hypnôse Drama Mascara excels in every aspect. Whether you want voluminous, curled, lengthened lashes or a mascara that's easy to apply and remove, this product delivers outstanding results. I have always been a fan of Lancome mascara formulas and  Lancôme Hypnôse Drama Mascara is hands down, my new favorite!
faceoff_positive.headline: The mascara you'll want on auto replenish!

faceoff_negative.comments: I received this product for free from Lancôme via Bzzagent in exchange for my honest review. My lashes are short, thin, and flat. They grow downwards and don't naturally curl up. Before applying mascara I always curl them so they look pretty and don't get in my eyes. After trying this product I can honestly say this mascara is not for me. That's not to say it's a bad product. I think it absolutely delivers on its promise of extreme volume. As you can see from the image with my eyes closed it makes my lashes thick, dark, and long compared to my other eye without mascara. My lashes look twice as long! That is a plus. However it added so much weight to my already small and thin lashes that they completely went flat and started going down towards my lower eyelid. I even tried curling them after application and the same thing happened. I also used the opening of the mascara container to wipe off excess product (something I always do) and it was still too much. I think this product is great for people with naturally curly lashes or who don't have trouble getting them to stay up. I would not purchase this on my own and considering the price I would not recommend knowing there are drugstore brands that are less expensive and effective. I also want to add the applicator brush looks neat but the bristles were too spaced apart. I prefer one with tighter bristles because this brush left globs of product on my lashes that I had to comb out with an eyelash tool. Many mascaras have a similar shaped curved brush so I don't understand the price of this product other than you're paying extra for brand name recognition. I was very disappointed considering I have another Lancôme mascara and I don't get as many issues with that one.
faceoff_negative.headline: Great volume but too much weight
